title: "Long Slow Exhale" w/ Rose Rollins
itunes:title: "Long Slow Exhale" w/ Rose Rollins
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate and Leisha are joined again by their good friend and “The L Word” castmate, Rose Rollins. Together they ask the hard-hitting questions like when will Rose return to Los Angeles? What is her show Spectrum “Long Slow Exhale” all about? And when did Alice and Tasha break up?


Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod

Email us: kateandleisha@gmail.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx

Artwork: Lovefoxxx
